Mix meat and 2 Tbsp. of the dressing. Shape into 4 patties. Spray large nonstick skillet with cooking spray. Add patties; cook on medium heat 5 min. on each side or until cooked through (160 degrees F.) Top with 2% Milk Singles; cook 1 min. or until melted. Serve in buns with lettuce, tomato and remaining 2 Tbsp. dressing.